data.description: Nicely remodeled and completely renovated. 4 Bedroom 2 Bath Brick Ranch Style home.  Open floor plan with a huge living area, big dining room and large country kitchen.  Split bedrooms with master bedroom on one end and other on the other end. Metal Roof. Like new home that even has new windows. Located in small town of Bonifay, Florida. Only 45 miles to Panama City Beach with the world's most beautiful beaches. Move In Ready. Proof of Funds or Prequalification Required. Check it out today!!!!!
